  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House", 
    "date": "2015-06-15T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Amends title II (Old Age, Survivors and Disability Insurance) (OASDI) of the Social Security Act to provide for full benefits for disabled widows and widowers without regard to age or any previous reduction in OASDI benefits.\n\nDeclares that there shall be no reduction in the widow's or widower's insurance benefit of an individual for any month in which such individual is under a disability."
